data.description: Enjoy the perfect combination of country and city in This well-maintained split-level home situated on a beautiful 1.59-acre lot in the highly sought-after Deerfield Estates. The exterior with vinyl siding, ensuring durability and minimal maintenance.?As you enter the home, you will be greeted with a spacious and open floor plan, with a vaulted ceiling. The kitchen is equipped with an eat-in breakfast bar. Main bedroom is complete with a walk-in closet, and main bathroom is roomy and well-appointed. You will also appreciate the convenience of the spacious laundry room and ample storage space throughout the home. The lower level features a cozy family room with a fireplace, along with two additional bedrooms and a bathroom. Step outside to a huge yard, perfect for entertaining friends and family. The deck off of the dining room provides a great spot for relaxation. A smoke shack in back is perfect for outdoor entertaining. You will appreciate the upgrades and cozy touches throughout.
